From 5b8afb4f949753e366d7116aa35bca45140cad73 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Adwait Nayak <adwaitn@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Sat, 19 Jul 2025 00:18:13 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:DP: wifi: ath12k: Add support for RX pktlog filter
 setting

This change mainly takes care of the filter setting support for
Rx pktlog.

Change description:
-> Add debugfs support for enabling various pktlog modes
   (full/ lite) and multiple pktlog TX filters (RCU/RCF/PHY)
-> Add support to subscribe Rx Monitor TLVs needed for pktlog,
   using current monitor framework.
-> Subscription model added for pktlog full (rx), pktlog lite (rx)
-> Handlers introduced to reset the pktlog filters to handle the
   disable or reset case.
-> Disable compaction, when pktlog is enabled

Signed-off-by: Adwait Nayak <adwaitn@qti.qualcomm.com>
